rComments: Professor Almas just makes boring concepts approachable and interesting. He loves to engage in class debates about the topics, and then I find myself trying my best to poke holes in the debates and interacting with the class material. He changes the formats of his lectures and ask trivia questions to keep everyone on their toes. My favourite prof.
I took the class because Almas was teaching and it was no let down. Though the matieral in itself isnt too interesting, he tries to engage with the class and his tests are always easy.

He has lots of personal experience in the field and makes every effort to show his student how to enter the geo/env field with job postings and resources to use. 393 was a great course, interesting material that is very beneficial in the real env field. The prof is approachable and a real nice guy.

I very much appreciate having him as my prof.. very nice and approachable. He is a practical prof who connects  course materials with real life work practices and experiences. He LOVES group projects!  I would highly recommend him! and wish him all the best in his career.
Really good prof.....easy to talk to, and always very interested in the lecture material. Especially liked how he tied the material into to working in the field.
Super nice professor that made the material exciting by using real world examples and getting student participation.
